    <PrimAttribute name="previouslyTracked" id="fce42f78-41c0-4dd8-bd07-3f238965f722">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Boolean"/>
        <access>readonly</access>
        <text>
This field is used to indicate if the record was previously being tracked before this change/delete
was applied.
When a transaction is aborted, this will determine whether to delete the record as it didn't previously
exist before this (aborted) transaction created it, or to restore it to it's prior state.</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
    <PrimAttribute name="priorChangeAction" id="f964e367-7eb0-455b-b6d6-275ed120c7bf">
